schools.name: Dr. Martin Luther King, Jr. Early College

data.description: Beautiful up-to-date 2 Bed | 2 Bath ranch home with Oakwood Homes signature smart space upstairs (providing ADDITIONAL living/flex space). This two-bedroom, two-bath features the main level master with a walk-in closet and four-piece master bath, a guest bedroom also with a walk-in closet, just steps from a full bathroom. A Beautiful open floor plan illustrates the kitchen with an island that opens to the dining room and great room; the kitchen is equipped with a large pantry that will include all appliances (stove, microwave, dishwasher, and refrigerator), and the laundry room. The great room sits on the east side of the home with beautiful large windows soaked with natural light that gives a wonderful view of the backyard that is equipped with an entertaining deck/patio. Upstairs, Oakwood's smart space, open for your use as desired and includes your utility room with the furnace and water heater.  Shopping includes grocery stores, numerous restaurants, banks, gas stations, etc. all within walking distance.  One of the fastest growing, and highest appreciating neighborhoods in Denver.  Perfect for first-time homebuyers, growing families, and investors.
